<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201204/bfb3c85bfa2f424abf9554856c815eec.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在济南市莱芜区的南部山区有一条旅游大道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>东起高庄街道后坡村，西至牛泉镇圣井村</strong>，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">全长30.5公里，贯穿23个自然村，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">整条旅游大道顺“势”造路、依“势”造景，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">营造出<strong>“车在路上走，人在画中游”</strong>的美好意境。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201204/e59cec733b284b60bcb684470960dbc2.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201204/deaff2e5276549bbb5a910128a346631.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
